title: Angellift  Dermastrips, 2 Medical Surgical Grade Non surgical Lifts,  Box
description: Angellift Dermastrips are a medically Recognized Anti-aging system with certified doctors from Tokyo to Beverly Hills.  Angellift Dermastrips are the over the counter version of Angellift Prescriptive, the first removable perioral implant fit by dentists and surgeons to correct the aging effects on the lower face.  Dermastrips have been proven to instantly eliminate the appearance of lower facial wrinkles by an average of 87% and are a proven comprehensive advancement over dermal injections.  Angellift Dermastrips are a completely natural dermal-filing technique to lift out aging lines.  The soft flexible perioral inserts remove wrinkles around the mouth and stimulate collagen growth as an alternative to surgery or injections.  The constant lift stimulates collagen growth as it lifts and levels the facial surface resetting position of the muscle and removing wrinkles.
